In today's fast-paced world, staying informed about local events and potential risks is crucial. Introducing TaB, the cutting-edge app that keeps you one step ahead of danger.

Your Personal Safety Radar
TaB harnesses the power of advanced web-scraping technology and real-time data analysis to provide you with up-to-the-minute information on events happening around you. From natural disasters to traffic incidents, TaB has you covered.

Key Features:
1. Event Tracking (Personal/Group): Our sophisticated algorithms continuously scan the web, bringing you the latest information on local and global events.
2. User-Friendly Design: Navigate through the app with ease, thanks to our sleek, intuitive interface designed for users of all tech levels.
3. Danger Assessment System: TaB doesn't just list events â€“ it analyzes them. Our proprietary risk assessment system categorizes each event's danger level, allowing you to make informed decisions quickly.

Futures:
Interactive Map Interface: Visualize events in your area with our intuitive map display. Zoom in, filter by event type, and get a bird's-eye view of your surroundings.
Customizable Alerts: Set up personalized notifications for the events and areas that matter most to you. Stay informed without being overwhelmed.
Comprehensive Event Details: Get in-depth information on each event, including real-time updates, official advisories, and community reports.
